00:04:37.820 --> 00:04:38.497 align:middle line:90%
People riot.

00:04:38.497 --> 00:04:39.080 align:middle line:90%
>>MALOOF: Yes.

00:04:39.080 --> 00:04:40.190 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: People loot.

00:04:40.190 --> 00:04:43.247 align:middle line:84%
They do all these other
