00:04:43.247 --> 00:04:43.830 align:middle line:90%
>>MALOOF: Yes.

00:04:43.830 --> 00:04:48.900 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: This would be--
gosh-- under biblical terms,

00:04:48.900 --> 00:04:50.040 align:middle line:90%
a catastrophe.

00:04:50.040 --> 00:04:51.020 align:middle line:90%
>>MALOOF: It would be.

00:04:51.020 --> 00:04:55.020 align:middle line:84%
And it would-- and
again, your urban centers

00:04:55.020 --> 00:04:56.120 align:middle line:90%
