problems emerging,

00:04:58.530 --> 00:05:00.690 align:middle line:90%
such as disease.

00:05:00.690 --> 00:05:01.930 align:middle line:90%
Sanitation problems.

00:05:01.930 --> 00:05:04.270 align:middle line:90%
