00:05:30.870 --> 00:05:33.880 align:middle line:84%
And we have to rely on
distribution systems, which

00:05:33.880 --> 00:05:37.730 align:middle line:84%
are all automated in many
cases, to deliver those food

00:05:37.730 --> 00:05:42.040 align:middle line:84%
and water and other supplies,
including medication.

00:05:42.040 --> 00:05:46.350 align:middle line:84%
People have maybe, at most,
30 days of their prescription

00:05:46.350 --> 00:05:47.030 align:middle line:90%
